                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17971206-26-defend293 t17971206-26-punish144"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 20.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice GROSE.</p>
